      m_Calls: []
  m_text: My lolo used to tell me stories about this mountain. He said Gugurang watches
    everything. Every step. Every breath. Every offering thrown into his fire. I
    thought they were just stories. Old tales to scare children into being good.
    So I walked up here with empty hands. No sacrifice. No prayer. Just... curiosity.
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2180264, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
